PN,46502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FIn an eight-day trial, Mold Crown
OL,8,FCourt heard how Abubakr, 30, and Umar,
OL,9,F34 were driving home from Aberystwyth
OL,10,Fto Manchester in separate cars when
OL,11,Fthey started to race one another.
OL,13,FWitnesses said they had seen the
OL,14,Fbrothers complete highly dangerous
OL,15,Fovertakes along the stretch of road,
OL,16,Fdriving at excessive speed,
OL,17,Ftailgating, and flashing their
OL,18,Fheadlights at other cars in an attempt
OL,19,Fto get past.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FShortly after both brothers took a
OL,8,Fbend in the road on the wrong side of
OL,9,Fthe carriageway, Abubakr's BMW
OL,10,Fcollided head-on with a Toyota being
OL,11,Fdriven by Rhys Jenkins on the Belan
OL,12,Fstraight.
OL,14,FAs other drivers stopped to help the
OL,15,Fdad and his son, both the brothers
OL,16,Ffled the scene in Umar's Audi S4.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FEmergency services attended, and Mr
OL,8,FJenkins was tragically confirmed to
OL,9,Fhave died from catastrophic injuries.
OL,10,FHis nine-year-old son, who had been a
OL,11,Fpassenger in the car, was air lifted
OL,12,Fto hospital, where he spent 10 days
OL,13,Fbeing treated for his injuries.
OL,15,FWithin 40 minutes of the collision, 34-
OL,16,Fyear-old Umar Yusaf drove back to the
OL,17,Fscene and told a PCSO the person
OL,18,Fresponsible was with him.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
