CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FThe brothers were arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving, and an
OL,10,Finvestigation was launched by Dyfed-
OL,11,FPowys Police's Serious Collision
OL,12,FInvestigation Unit.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FStatements from a number of witnesses
OL,8,Fdescribed the brothers' manner of
OL,9,Fdriving as 'reckless', 'erratic', and
OL,10,Fconsistent with racing. It was
OL,11,Fdetermined that while Umar's car was
OL,12,Fnot directly involved in the
OL,13,Fcollision, the 'competitive' nature of
OL,14,Fhis driving with his brother
OL,15,Fcontributed significantly to the fatal
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FThe brothers were charged with causing
OL,8,Fdeath by dangerous driving, causing
OL,9,Fserious injury by dangerous driving,
OL,10,Fand failing to stop after a road
OL,11,Ftraffic collision.
OL,13,FAbubakr Yusaf was also charged with
OL,14,Fcausing death while uninsured, drug
OL,15,Fdriving and failing to provide a
OL,16,Fspecimen for analysis.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FAbubakr Yusaf was today found guilty
OL,8,Fof causing death by dangerous driving,
OL,9,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,10,Fdriving and causing death whilst
OL,11,Funinsured.
OL,13,FUmar Yusaf was found guilty of causing
OL,14,Fdeath by careless driving and causing
OL,15,Fserious injury by careless driving.
OL,17,FThey will be sentenced on Monday 27
OL,18,FJuly 2026.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FRhys's wife, Carrie Jenkins, said:
OL,8,F"Following the conviction, I would
OL,9,Flike to thank the court, the jury, the
OL,10,FCPS, police and all those involved in
OL,11,Fthis trial, including the many
OL,12,Fwitnesses who came forward.
OL,14,F"The loss of Rhys in such an
OL,15,Funexpected and unnecessary way has
OL,16,Fbeen devastating, but our focus as a
OL,17,Ffamily has been to rebuild our lives,
OL,18,Fand to make the most of each day, as
OL,19,FRhys would have wanted, with the
OL,20,Fsupport of our friends and community.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,F"I hope the publicity surrounding the
OL,8,FCrown Court case highlights to others
OL,9,Fthe dangers of driving at speed, and
OL,10,Facts as a reminder that we all have a
OL,11,Fresponsibility when we get behind a
OL,12,Fwheel."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
