PN,46511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FJoanne Brine, solicitor for Carrie
OL,8,FJenkins said: "This has been an
OL,9,Funimaginably distressing time for Mrs
OL,10,FJenkins, coping with a life-changing
OL,11,Fsituation which she has handled with
OL,12,Fcourage and grace as she, her children
OL,13,Fand their wider family have come to
OL,14,Fterms with the devastating loss of a
OL,15,Fmuch-loved husband and father.
OL,26,@pD@OOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/12
