OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1781294762
OL,3,CBrothers guilty of killing man and
OL,4,Cseriously injuring son in 'reckless'
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,F"Nothing will ever heal the
OL,8,Foverwhelming pain of his loss, but
OL,9,Fthey continue to navigate their future
OL,10,Fin the best way possible, with the
OL,11,Finvaluable support of their wider
OL,12,Fcommunity.
OL,14,F"We will continue to support the
OL,15,Ffamily as they pursue civil redress
OL,16,Ffor the actions which lead to Rhys'
OL,17,Funtimely death."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@PO]
